{"tid":769314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優月入200萬YEN, 爸爸:十分支持她","createTime":"2018-08-06T05:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T09:17:05.000Z","uid":25345,"like":212,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"8142e7aec4cf85dce09b3b77dcf7c39a1edaf8cd","tid":769314,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"AV女優月撈200萬 爽住高級公寓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n22歲日本AV女優水川蓳近日受邀登上節目《給予明細》公開女優工作行程，甚至公開自己的薪資條，透露自己月拍10部片可領200萬日圓（約55萬台幣）酬勞。<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dR4RWP0Yqi5QjGRhi.7Ofw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjkx/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/26f24496505b96257a6f3da2bb45a0a6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdR4RWP0Yqi5QjGRhi.7Ofw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjkx%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F26f24496505b96257a6f3da2bb45a0a6&h=f2f34596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲水川蓳月拍10部片可拿200萬。（圖／翻攝自AbemaTV）<br />\n<br />\n水川蓳曾是片商「Prestige」的專屬女優，現在轉為個人企劃，日前節目組特的跟拍她的一日生活，從拍片事前化妝、簽同意書，與合作男優互換身體健康檢查報告，到拍攝成人片，下工領薪水，發現她一個月靠10支成人片作品，拿到約200萬日圓（約55萬台幣），平均一部5萬5的報酬。<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/D17kP3GzZJ6hpqRfSIAP0g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/a3ed19d4758e1c345696ec9a75a5c409\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FD17kP3GzZJ6hpqRfSIAP0g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fa3ed19d4758e1c345696ec9a75a5c409&h=3a8624b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲水川蓳爸爸很支持女兒事業。（圖／翻攝自AbemaTV）<br />\n<br />\n優渥的薪資讓水川蓳得以住在市區60坪2房1廳，陽台可以俯瞰東京鐵塔的高級公寓，節目最後也訪問了她的爸爸，對方不僅不反對女兒投身至成人片，甚至期許她能成為AV界的鈴木一朗。"},{"pid":"3b1d7519f2425f7d5d7233dde971b3c0aeb50c18","tid":769314,"uid":198242,"like":486,"dislike":2,"score":484,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"佢老豆有份買碟捧自己個女場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22092831734c1c13ebdc89f11759da669f649b1e","tid":769314,"uid":55386,"like":46,"dislike":4,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個樣咩事"},{"pid":"e48502ad738d3a95ddd497792518c591d3a53fff","tid":769314,"uid":49004,"like":151,"dislike":7,"score":144,"quote":{"pid":"3b1d7519f2425f7d5d7233dde971b3c0aeb50c18","tid":769314,"uid":198242,"like":486,"dislike":2,"score":484,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"佢老豆有份買碟捧自己個女場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"直接屌啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8011715ff3e36ea6986970f8d844fafaf47173aa","tid":769314,"uid":158172,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:50:48.000Z","msg":"死魚一條"},{"pid":"dcf1b177cf68ae7a7fcbf56d2efdaafe79251848","tid":769314,"uid":73613,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0006b850528faba00869c5914570dad231d39121","tid":769314,"uid":21460,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"一個月十套都幾辛苦"},{"pid":"49e722ed1c88624bf2f9584c4d42139a16811756","tid":769314,"uid":67823,"like":276,"dislike":72,"score":204,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"日本人好尊重av女優<br />\n佢地覺得女優為大和民族男人服務好光榮<br />\nav女優家人亦覺得光宗耀祖"},{"pid":"4fba98baa5ace437ab268f7372d4423a3be999de","tid":769314,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3b1d7519f2425f7d5d7233dde971b3c0aeb50c18","tid":769314,"uid":198242,"like":486,"dislike":2,"score":484,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2