dBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"其實日本人好多蟲"},{"pid":"37d85c0bc28b32be4dc7d4d17e2aa9efc71c4940","tid":769314,"uid":43809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"拍套近親相姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9949b5c0266951f6ba36a778c0e44f1504ae17","tid":769314,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"好難想像親人拍av係點"},{"pid":"a36824fdb0761d6be49da612e30eaac8f3bf0502","tid":769314,"uid":14497,"like":258,"dislike":14,"score":244,"quote":{"pid":"058ce2fd08bebda06df82c25b20891727ec6c10f","tid":769314,"uid":44333,"like":216,"dislike":2,"score":214,"quote":{"pid":"9a5d1ecf034d6694b72b4e63155e2eb8cc18ecc0","tid":769314,"uid":14497,"like":310,"dislike":2,"score":308,"quote":{"pid":"dc8afd6568333996892ba7e89cacdb23751caed8","tid":769314,"uid":33655,"like":345,"dislike":2,"score":343,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"但係三文魚會食日本人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"真正既三文魚係唔會食日本人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"其實日本人好多蟲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"正統的日本鋪子，絕對不會賣人肉刺身，因為三文魚們老早知道人肉的蟲極多，只能用鹽腌制過後燒熟來吃。<br />\n<br />\n吃活人，有個原則，那就是只吃深海的，而且要生長在溫帶或寒帶之中，靠近熱帶的人都不能吃。和我們以為一活就可以拿來做刺身，完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n日本人會游到淡水的河中產卵，是一大禁忌。當然，淡水如果不受污染的話，還能養出能生吃的日本人來，但當今的河流，有哪一條是乾淨的呢？"},{"pid":"68a84ad5f43030a60f445eb5b0cd5e527d33ded1","tid":769314,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"咁嘅樣都有200萬羊一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120e9bb8595eecc40bea2c126ed15803b7c266d8","tid":769314,"uid":22701,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"計返一套先得$14000 HKD  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635d7963e4c5c3edbad1099d390def82e38b29db","tid":769314,"uid":12363,"